==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Interagency
<hw>In`ter*a"gen*cy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to actions, processes, or objects involving to more than one
agency (senses 4 or 5); <as>as, <ex>interagency</ex>
cooperation</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Interagency</ent>⟦br⟧

